caption: The image is a colorful poster featuring a pizza and a hamburger. The text on the poster reads "Will Draw for Food," indicating that the poster is promoting a fundraising event for the San Bruno Food Bank. The poster is likely aiming to attract attention and encourage donations to support the cause.
